  <summary>1/4/1995--Introduced.
Neutral Cost Recovery Act of 1995 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow the depreciation deduction to be computed based on a neutral recovery basis for certain property placed in service after December 31, 1994. Increases the dollar limitation on the deduction to expense depreciable business assets.</summary>
